+# /SOT.md — A2rchitech Source of Truth (v0)
+
+Generated: 2026-01-27
+
+---
+
+## 0. Purpose
+
+This document is the single starting anchor for the A2rchitech rebuild:
+
+• consolidates session law  
+• defines the AgenticOS north star  
+• locks invariants  
+• indexes historical sessions  
+• provides the authoritative roadmap  
+
+Everything else links *into* this file.
+
+---
+
+## 1. Identity
+
+A2rchitech is an **AgenticOS engineering platform**:
+
+- personal operator desktop  
+- enterprise SaaS cockpit  
+- swarm orchestration workspace  
+- DAG‑native execution harness  
+- multi‑LLM router  
+- deterministic automation engine  
+
+---
+
+## 2. Platform Laws (Non‑Negotiable)
+
+1. Deterministic boot (B0): `/SOT.md`, specs, contracts, CODEBASE first.
+2. Task DAG is the primary abstraction.
+3. Every node carries WIH / Beads.
+4. Claude‑Tasks parity engine is built *inside* A2R.
+5. Pre‑tool hooks enforce policy.
+6. All artifacts live under `/.a2r/`.
+7. Single kernel; many UI/CLI surfaces.
+8. One gateway endpoint; no port sprawl.
+9. Layered memory + promotion gates.
+10. Reproducibility + audit receipts mandatory.
+
+---
+
+## 3. Canonical Workflow
+
+Boot → Load Law → Load Task Graph → Validate WIH → Spawn Environment → Execute → Record Receipts → Promote Learnings → Resume or Terminate.
+
+---
+
+## 4. Session Consolidation Rule
+
+Spoken command:
+
+> gizzi save a2r session
+
+Produces:
+
+- markdown export
+- deltas
+- conflicts
+- decisions
+- unresolved questions
+
+Merged into the canonical buildout thread.
+
+---
+
+## 5. Source Documents
+
+- A2R_CONTINUATION_PLAN.md  
+- A2R_SESSION_EXTRACTS_B1.md  
+- A2R_SESSION_EXTRACTS_B2.md  
+- A2R_CONFLICT_REGISTER.md  
+- A2R_GAP_MATRIX.md  
+- A2R_DIRECTION_VECTOR.md  
+- A2R_MASTER_ROADMAP.md  
+
+---
+
+## 6. Direction Vector
+
+North star:
+
+- daily workspace for humans + agents  
+- deterministic production automation  
+- enterprise‑grade orchestration  
+- optional crypto + social layers after core harness  
+
+---
+
+## 7. Roadmap Summary
+
+### Phase 0 — Law Layer
+• SOT.md  
+• CODEBASE.md  
+• WIH schema  
+• ADR registry  
+
+### Phase 1 — Tasks Engine
+• DAG scheduler  
+• /install & /resume  
+• environment snapshots  
+
+### Phase 2 — Enforcement
+• tool gates  
+• path guards  
+• provenance receipts  
+
+### Phase 3 — Memory
+• layered memory  
+• RLM promotion  
+• proposal store  
+
+### Phase 4 — Networking
+• single gateway  
+• service discovery  
+
+### Phase 5 — UI Cockpit
+• workspace home  
+• DAG inspector  
+• replay + audits  
+
+### Phase 6 — Multi‑LLM Router
+• policy driven  
+• cost caps  
+• audit logs  
+
+---
+
+## 8. Next Action
+
+This file becomes `/SOT.md` once accepted.
+
+All new specs reference this seed.
+
+---
+
+END.
